comments: Nembhard (IND) is reaching for the ball and marginal contact occurs between his face and Jokic's (DEN) left arm.
Turner (IND) brings his hand toward Jokic's (DEN) path and marginal contact occurs near the sideline.
Turner (IND) is moving slightly toward Jokic's (DEN) path and marginal body contact occurs as Jokic leaves the floor to release the pass.
Nesmith (IND) and Murray (DEN) briefly tangle arms while attempting to secure the loose ball and marginal contact occurs before they disengage during the rebound.
Nesmith (IND) steps toward the loose ball and incidental contact occurs between the ball and his right leg.
Nembhard (IND) retreats in Murray's (DEN) path and marginal contact occurs as a result of Murray extending his right leg during his shooting motion.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a defensive goaltending by Turner (IND) is confirmed and IND is given possession of the ball. Turner blocks the shot attempt after the ball makes contact with the backboard and has a chance to score.
Porter Jr. (DEN) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes OOB.
Turner (IND) reaches for the pass and marginal contact occurs with Jokic's (DEN) left arm as he secures the ball.
Murray (DEN) retreats in Nesmith's (IND) path and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs while making clean contact with the ball during the driving shot attempt.
Porter Jr. (DEN) blocks the ball OOB.
Gordon (DEN) rests a slight hand on Siakam's (IND) side while adjusting alongside his path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) is reaching for the loose ball and marginal contact occurs with Siakam's (IND) arms after he secures the ball for the shot attempt at the basket.
Nesmith (IND) slightly extends his forearm to release away from Caldwell-Pope (DEN) as the pass is made and the contact is marginal.
